01:48.530 --> 01:50.530
All right, all right,
all right, knock it off!

01:50.530 --> 01:51.530
Knock it off!

01:51.530 --> 01:53.400
Fonzie's right.

01:53.400 --> 01:55.480
FONZIE:
All right, get these guys
started on the next chapter.

01:55.480 --> 01:56.980
Watch them; they
will try anything.

01:56.980 --> 01:58.070
RICHIE:
Right.

01:58.070 --> 01:59.150
I got business.

01:59.150 --> 02:01.070
You can depend on me, Fonz;
I'll watch these guys.

02:01.070 --> 02:03.160
Yeah.
(chuckles)

02:07.160 --> 02:08.660
Let's get
out of here!
Huh? What? What? What?

02:08.660 --> 02:10.160
Come on.
What are you doing?

02:10.160 --> 02:11.660
I thought you were
supposed to watch us.

02:11.660 --> 02:13.170
I was faking!

02:13.170 --> 02:14.670
I'd lie to my grandmother
for sleep.

02:14.670 --> 02:16.170
Let's get out of here.
All right.

